query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('axiom-of-choice',
'binomial-theorem',
'connectedness',
'education',
'geometric-topology',
'group-actions',
'juju',
'limsup-and-liminf',
'normal-subgroups',
'numerical-linear-algebra',
'power-management',
'random-walk',
'solution-verification',
'tensors',
'vector-fields')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 10 AND u1.downvotes <= 100000
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Autobiographer',
'Caucus',
'Citizen Patrol',
'Critic',
'Good Question',
'Necromancer',
'Organizer',
'Revival',
'Supporter',
'Teacher') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
